---
import SectionLabel from "../../elements/SectionLabel.astro";
import Heading from "../../elements/Heading.astro";
import BodyText from "../../elements/BodyText.astro";
---

<section
  class="bg-rh-warm-light dark:bg-rh-warm-dark py-28 md:py-40 px-6 md:px-10"
  id="analysis-section"
>
  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-[1400px]">
    <!-- Terminal Header -->
    <div class="analysis-reveal mb-10">
      <SectionLabel text="> SYS.ANALYSIS // PATTERN_RECOGNIZED" />
    </div>

    <!-- Headline -->
    <Heading class="analysis-reveal mb-12 max-w-5xl">
      Every revolution breaks the humans
      <span class="text-rh-ember">first.</span>
    </Heading>

    <!-- Context -->
    <div class="analysis-reveal max-w-3xl mb-16">
      <BodyText>
        This isn't new. Every revolution in how we work has followed the same
        pattern: the tools change first. The human systems get figured out later,
        painfully, expensively, after enormous damage.
      </BodyText>
    </div>

    <!-- Revolution Examples -->
    <div class="max-w-4xl space-y-14 mb-20">
      <!-- Industrial Revolution -->
      <div class="analysis-era">
        <p
          class="font-mono text-xs md:text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-rh-ember mb-4"
        >
          The Industrial Revolution
        </p>
        <BodyText>
          Mechanized production. It took decades of exploitation, children in
          factories and workers without rights, before anyone designed the human
          protections the new era required.
        </BodyText>
      </div>

      <!-- Knowledge Economy -->
      <div class="analysis-era">
        <p
          class="font-mono text-xs md:text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-rh-ember mb-4"
        >
          The Knowledge Economy
        </p>
        <BodyText>
          Connected information. It took a generation before most people had
          access to the networks and credentials that actually determined who got
          ahead.
        </BodyText>
      </div>

      <!-- AI Revolution - longest, most visceral -->
      <div class="analysis-era">
        <p
          class="font-mono text-xs md:text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-rh-ember mb-4"
        >
          The AI Revolution
        </p>
        <BodyText class="mb-4">
          Automating cognition. Entire teams eliminated overnight. Roles that
          held organizations together, gone. The people who carried culture,
          onboarded through relationships, connected humans to each other -
          replaced by tools that can't do any of that.
        </BodyText>
        <BodyText>
          The tools are moving faster than ever. The human side hasn't even
          started.
        </BodyText>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- The Gap - key line, visually isolated -->
    <div class="analysis-reveal max-w-4xl mb-10">
      <p
        class="font-heading text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black uppercase italic tracking-tight leading-none text-rh-ink dark:text-rh-chalk"
      >
        We are in the <span class="text-rh-ember">gap</span> right now.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="analysis-reveal max-w-3xl mb-6">
      <BodyText>
        The window between the tool change and the human redesign. That's where
        the damage happens.
      </BodyText>
    </div>

    <!-- The Turn -->
    <div class="analysis-reveal max-w-3xl mb-12">
      <p
        class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-heading font-bold text-rh-ink dark:text-rh-chalk leading-snug"
      >
        Every previous revolution, we waited.<br /><br />
        This time, we don't have to.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="analysis-reveal">
      <a
        href="/thesis"
        class="inline-block font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-rh-ember hover:underline"
      >
        Read the Full Thesis →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  import { gsap } from "gsap";
  import { ScrollTrigger } from "gsap/ScrollTrigger";
  gsap.registerPlugin(ScrollTrigger);

  gsap.fromTo(
    ".analysis-reveal",
    { opacity: 0, y: 50 },
    {
      opacity: 1,
      y: 0,
      duration: 1,
      stagger: 0.3,
      ease: "power3.out",
      scrollTrigger: {
        trigger: "#analysis-section",
        start: "top 70%",
      },
    },
  );

  gsap.fromTo(
    ".analysis-era",
    { opacity: 0, x: -20 },
    {
      opacity: 1,
      x: 0,
      duration: 0.8,
      stagger: 0.2,
      ease: "power2.out",
      scrollTrigger: {
        trigger: "#analysis-section",
        start: "top 55%",
      },
    },
  );
</script>
